{"tid":1451341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:23:20.000Z","uid":80329,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0dcf21d62de48ec0c36235aeabd2725e9b0d48c3","tid":1451341,"uid":80329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:49:50.000Z","msg":"一人一Post狂洗連登 [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaNagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=c02ef63b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaNagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=1b151b76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"4be323c8ef7155ec6388390b371675be7a7b3c38","tid":1451341,"uid":283109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:50:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">機場文宣整合post</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1450351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1450351</a><br />\n<br />\n「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場"},{"pid":"d79f9a8c91b466d50c301ba3f8a6c7be162b0fb6","tid":1451341,"uid":167467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:50:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請帶備更換衣物及梳洗用品入機場</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"ht